  10,9,"Surely those who believe and do good, their Lord will guide them ňĻto Paradiseňļ through their faith, rivers will flow under their feet in the Gardens of Bliss"
  10,10,"in which their prayer will be, ‚ÄúGlory be to You, O Allah!‚ÄĚ and their greeting will be, ‚ÄúPeace!‚ÄĚ and their closing prayer will be, ‚ÄúAll praise is for Allah‚ÄĒLord of all worlds!‚ÄĚ"